      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NUGGET NED (1) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 2.25 lengths into third (18.36) at Richmond in a Grade 5 over 320m. Top chance in this line up. TAYLOR MADE BLUE (4) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (19.33) last time out at this track. Has good early speed so he should be prominent despite the squeeze draw. Can feature again. REAL EXPRESS (3) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (18.64) last time in a Grade 5 at Richmond. Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of four starts. Expected to give a good account. RAY FINKLE (2) is worth including.",
